FBIS4-14040 "drnes080_n_94004" FBIS-NES-94-080 Daily Report 25 Apr 1994 LEBANON Iran Requests Information on Missing Diplomats Iran Requests Information on Missing Diplomats NC2504131094 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1030 GMT 25 Apr 94 NC2504131094 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Excerpt] Iranian Ambassador in Lebanon Homayun 'Alizadeh conveyed a verbal message to Foreign Minister Faris Buwayz from the Iranian Government today. The message requests information about the fate of Iranian diplomats [who disappeared in 1982] at a Lebanese Forces checkpoint. [passage omitted]
